{"id":474278113,"lang":"cpp","time":"5 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1617110019,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/474278113/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"6.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        int freq[256]={0};       \n        int j=0;\n        int n=s.length();\n        int len=1;\n        for(int i=0;i<n;i++)\n        {            \n            while(j<n && freq[s[j]]==0)\n            {\n                freq[s[j]]++;\n                j++;                \n            }\n            len=max(j-i+1,len);\n            freq[s[i]]--;\n        }\n        return len-1;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
